a]]\n| Decision (unanimous)\n| [[UFC on Fox: dos Santos vs. Miocic]]\n| {{dts|2014|December|13|format=mdy}}\n| align=center | 3\n| align=center | 5:00\n| [[Phoenix, Arizona]], United States\n| {{small|Return to Bantamweight.}}\n|-\n| {{yes2}}Win\n| align=center | 6\u20130\n|  Elias Garcia\n| Decision (unanimous)\n| Legacy FC 27\n| {{dts|2014|January|31|format=mdy}}\n| align=center | 3\n| align=center | 5:00\n| [[Houston, Texas]], United States\n| {{small|Flyweight debut; Cejudo missed weight (128.5 lbs).}}\n|-\n| {{yes2}}Win\n| align=center | 5\u20130\n| Ryan Hollis\n| Decision (unanimous)\n| Legacy FC 24\n| {{dts|2013|October|11|format=mdy}}\n| align=center | 3\n| align=center | 5:00\n| [[Dallas, Texas]], United States\n| {{small|Catchweight (128 lbs) bout.}}\n|-\n| {{yes2}}Win\n| align=center | 4\u20130\n| Miguelito Marti\n| TKO (punches)\n| Gladiator Challenge: American Dream\n| {{dts|2013|5|18}}\n| align=center | 1\n| align=center | 1:43\n| [[Lincoln, California]], United States\n|\n|-\n| {{yes2}}Win\n| align=center | 3\u20130\n| Anthony Sessions\n| TKO (punches)\n| WFF 10: Cejudo v Sessions\n| {{dts|2013|4|19}}\n| align=center | 1\n| align=center | 4:23\n| [[Chandler, Arizona]], United States\n| {{small|Won the WFF Bantamweight Championship.}}\n|-\n| {{yes2}}Win\n| align=center | 2\u20130\n| Sean Henry Barnett\n| TKO (punches)\n| Gladiator Challenge: Battleground\n| {{dts|2013|3|24}}\n| align=center | 1\n| align=center | 4:55\n| [[San Jacinto, California]], United States\n|\n|-\n| {{yes2}}Win\n| align=center | 1\u20130\n| Michael Poe\n| TKO (punches)\n| WFF MMA: Pascua Yaqui Fights 4\n| {{dts|2013|3|2}}\n| align=center | 1\n| align=center | 1:25\n| [[Tucson, Arizona]], United States\n|\n{{end}}\n<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sherdog.com/fighter/Henry-Cejudo-125297|title=Henry|last=Sherdog.com|website=Sherdog|access-date=November 11, 2018}}</ref>\n\n==Freestyle record==\n{{s-start}}\n|-\n! colspan=\"7\"| World Championships & Olympic Games Matches\n|-\n!  Res.\