 verbannt \"Die Pyramide\" ins Nachtprogramm|website=Dwdl.de|url=http://www.dwdl.de/nachrichten/37520/zdf_verbannt_die_pyramide_ins_nachtprogramm/|format=|accessdate=2012-10-07|last=Uwe Mantel|date=2012-09-16|year= |language=German|pages=|quote=}}</ref>\n| [[:de:Die Pyramide (Fernsehsendung)|Die Pyramide]]\n| [[Dieter Thomas Heck]]<br />[[:de:Micky Beisenherz|Micky Beisenherz]] and [[:de:Joachim Llambi|Joachim Llambi]]\n| [[ZDF]]<br />[[ZDFneo]]\n| 1978\u201394<br />2012 \n|-\n| Hast Du Worte?\n| [[:de:J\u00f6rg Pilawa|J\u00f6rg Pilawa]] (1996\u201397)<br />[[:de:Thomas Koschwitz|Thomas Koschwitz]] (1997\u201399)\n| [[Sat.1]]\n| 1996\u201399\n|-\n|rowspan=2 |{{flag|Indonesia}}\n| [[:id:Piramida (kuis)|Piramida]]\n| Ronnie Sianturi<br />Ricky Johannes\n|rowspan=2 |[[RCTI]]\n| 1995\u201399<br />2000\n|-\n| [[:id:Piramida Baru|Piramida Baru]]'''\n| Ricky Johannes\n| 2001\u201303\n|-\n| {{flag|Iran}}\n| Pyramid'''\n| Sina Valiollah\n| [[Persian Music Channel|PMC]]\n| 2009\n|-\n| rowspan=2|{{flag|Israel}}\n| \u05e9\u05d7\u05e7 \u05d0\u05d5\u05ea\u05d4<br />[[:he:\u05e9\u05d7\u05e7 \u05d0\u05d5\u05ea\u05d4|Play It]]\n| Yigal Shilon<br />[[Dudu Topaz]] \n| [[Channel 1 (Israel)|Channel 1]]\n| 1979\u201380<br>1983\u201384\n|-\n| \u05d4\u05e4\u05d9\u05e8\u05de\u05d9\u05d3\u05d4<br />HaPyramida'''\n| Oded Menashe\n| [[Channel 2 (Israel)|Channel 2]]\n| 2002\n|-\n| {{flag|Italy}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.televisionando.it/articolo/pyramid-debora-salvalaggio-e-enrico-brignano-nel-nuovo-game-show-di-rai-due/3105/| title=Pyramid - Chi mi capisce \u00e8 bravo|website=Televisionando.it}}</ref>\n| Pyramid \u2013 Chi mi capisce \u00e8 bravo\n| [[:it:Enrico Brignano|Enrico Brignano]] and [[:it:Debora Salvalaggio|Debora Salvalaggio]]\n| [[Rai Due]]\n| December 3, 2007 \u2013 February 3, 2008 \n|-\n| {{flag|Poland}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/ProgramyTV/photos/a.465651183544943/467058703404191/?type=3|title=Programy w TV, kt\u00f3re ka\u017cdy ogl\u0105da\u0142, ale 