ne Publishing|isbn=0-7567-2623-9}}\n* {{Cite book|url=https://catalogue.nla.gov.au/Record/3578859|title=Homeland Security Law and Policy|editor-last=Nicholson|editor-first=William C.|publisher=C. C Thomas|year=2005|isbn=0-398-07583-2|chapter=Foreword |author=Joseph Biden}}\n* {{Cite book|title=Promises to Keep|last=Biden|first=Joe|publisher=[[Random House]]|date=July 31, 2007|isbn=978-1-4000-6536-3|url=https://www.amazon.com/Promises-Keep-Politics-Joe-Biden/dp/1400065364/ref=tmm_hrd_swatch_0?_encoding=UTF8&qid=&sr=}} Also paperback edition, Random House 2008, {{ISBN|0-8129-7621-5}}.\n* {{Cite book|url=https://www.amazon.com/Promise-Me-Dad-Hardship-Purpose/dp/1250171679|title=Promise Me, Dad: A Year of Hope, Hardship, and Purpose |last=Biden |first=Joe |publisher=Flatiron Books |date=November 14, 2017 |isbn=978-1250171672}}\n{{Refend}}\n\n==See also==\n\n* [[Trump\u2013Ukraine scandal]]\n* [[List of things named after Joe Biden]]\n\n== Notes ==\n\n{{Reflist|30em|group=nb}}\n\n== References ==\n=== Footnotes ===\n\n{{Reflist|25em}}\n\n=== Books ===\n\n{{refbegin|30em}}\n* {{Cite book|title=The Almanac of American Politics |last = Barone |first = Michael | authorlink=Michael Barone (pundit) | first2= Richard E. | last2=Cohen | authorlink2 = Richard E. Cohen |year = 2008 |publisher = [[National Journal]] |location = Washington |isbn=978-0-89234-116-0|title-link = The Almanac of American Politics }}\n* {{cite book | last=Bronner | first=Ethan | authorlink=Ethan Bronner | title=Battle for Justice: How the Bork Nomination Shook America | publisher=[[W. W. Norton & Company]] | year=1989 | isbn=0-393-02690-6 | url=https://archive.org/details/battleforjustice00bron_0 }}\n* {{cite book | last=Gadsen | first=Brett | title=Between North and South: Delaware, Desegregation, and the Myth of American Sectionalism | url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ZFQE3bLDsS4C | date=October 8, 2012 | publisher=University of Pennsylvania Press | isbn=978-0-8122-0797-2 | ref=harv}}\n* {{cite boo